first api call from front end to below service 
api : https://iop-dev.nss.vzwnet.com:8080/rcmengine/switch/pathfinder/widget/banner/count?user_id=<user_id>

service name: rcmservice
service repo : https://gitlab.verizon.com/INTEGRATEDOPSPORTA/rcmservice/
second api call from backend rcmservice  to switch service
based on the below condition(checking user type)


if (role == 'SWITCH_MANAGER' || role == 'CELL_SWITCH_MANAGER') {
          url = config.switchService.url + 'mgr/' + userId;
        } else if (role == 'SWITCH_TECHNICIAN') {
          url = config.switchService.url + 'tech/' + userId;
        } else if (role == 'TRANSLATION_MANAGER' || role == 'TRANSLATION_ENGINEER') {
          url = config.switchService.url + 'trans/' + userId;


